sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant Database
    participant Validator
    
    Note over Admin,Validator: Question Creation & Verification Flow
    
    Admin->>Frontend: Fill question form
    Frontend->>Validator: Validate input
    Validator-->>Frontend: Validation passed
    
    Frontend->>API: POST /questions/create
    API->>Database: Check section & topic exist
    Database-->>API: Valid IDs
    
    API->>Database: Insert question (status=pending)
    Database-->>API: Question ID
    API-->>Frontend: Question created
    Frontend-->>Admin: Success message
    
    Note over Admin,Validator: Another Admin Verifies
    
    Admin->>Frontend: Open verification dashboard
    Frontend->>API: GET /questions?status=pending
    API->>Database: Fetch pending questions
    Database-->>API: List of questions
    API-->>Frontend: Questions list
    
    Admin->>Frontend: Review question
    
    alt Approve
        Admin->>Frontend: Click "Approve"
        Frontend->>API: PATCH /questions/{id}/approve
        API->>Database: Update status=approved, verifiedBy, verifiedAt
    else Reject
        Admin->>Frontend: Click "Reject" + reason
        Frontend->>API: PATCH /questions/{id}/reject
        API->>Database: Update status=rejected
    end
    
    Database-->>API: Updated
    API-->>Frontend: Status changed
    Frontend-->>Admin: Confirmation
